{"tid":368326,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[嚴打走資] 中央限企業境外投資！包括房地產、酒店同股權","createTime":"2017-08-21T12:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T13:40:10.000Z","uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0c9f432b11a63c1bbc947df45ea68b4794bbe9","tid":368326,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"[嚴打走資] 中央限企業境外投資！包括房地產、酒店同股權<br />\n2017-08-18 17:26:36 HKT<br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】國務院辦公廳今日發佈通知，稱已同意發改委、商務部、人行、外交部《關於進一步引導和規範境外投資方向的指導意見》，要求全國執行。文件稱將限制境內企業在境外投資房地產、酒店、影城、娛樂業、體育俱樂部，以及在境外設立無具體實業項目的股權投資基金或投資平臺。這類投資，均須須經境外投資主管部門核准。<br />\n<br />\n目前萬達、安邦、海航三大資本集團因在海外大肆收購，被指是轉移資產而飽受爭議。其中，萬達在海外購買投資大量酒店、影城、體育俱樂部；海航則在香港等地搶地，而安邦則購買大量基金公司、酒店。但文件未有提及，對這些已投資項目，將做如何處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57097795&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57097795%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170818&d=ZXOFqNCCuWIl91%2F%2FYo6SXpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d4f00a1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57097795%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170818&h=43c4f174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57097795&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170818</a>"},{"pid":"fa22ad6ddc718c44a1158bc39514c99448f67735","tid":368326,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}